messages.message: i searched for this in our codebase and realized that we have a webpage that sends feedback emails to this address (ex: https://dogfood.instabase.com/feedback)

i don’t think we link to this `/feedback` page anywhere, though

so i think it’s fine to delete this page (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/master/webserver/webapp/src/py/instabase/webapp/handler/views/home.py#L152) (it was created 7 years ago :open_mouth: )
Cool, I see a burst of emails to it around 3-22-2023 but that’s about it in recent memory
